body:
### Welcome to LSU Code Dojo.
LSU Code Dojo is a club which holds weekly meetings for getting together to code. Anyone with an interest in coding is welcome, whether you are a n00b or fully-grown neckbeard.


### Support or Contact
Please contact John Harvey (@GradientVector) for more information.
